string.value: #eDownhill Vault! Carefully choose your path down.\n#n<Note: Once you go down, you can't go back up.>

string.value: #eClimbing Vault! Scale the monster columns to reach the top.\n#n<Note: Approach a column, jump and press the up arrow key to climb the column.>

string.name: info
string.value: #eBurning Vault! Keep jumping to reach the top.\n#n<Note: You can move up and down using the basic jump move.>

string.name: info
string.value: #eSpring Vault! Use the springs get around.\n#n<Note: Stepping on a spring will send you flying.>

string.name: info

string.value: A small sprout is growing in the Bellflower Pot. It sways happily from side to side.

string.name: text
string.value: A small sprout is growing in the Bellflower Pot. It sways happily from side to side.

string.name: text
string.value: A Baby Bellflower peaks out from the pot. Its bright, sparkly eyes gaze out at the world with wonder.

string.name: text
string.value: Whoa! It's a Golden Bellflower! Its curious smile fills you with pride and happiness.

string.name: text
string.value: It looks like your Baby Bellflower is all grown up. It's almost time to send them home, but you know they'll never forget you.

string.name: text
string.value: It looks like your Golden Baby Bellflower is all grown up. It's almost time to send them home. Shh. No tears, only dreams now.

string.name: text
string.value: The Baby Bellflower left you a gift straight from the heart. Hurry and open your present!

string.name: text
string.value: The Golden Baby Bellflower left lovely gift. Hurry and open your present!

string.name: text
string.value: It looks like none of the Bellflower seeds will be sprouting today. Let's check back tomorrow.
